title: ISS astronaut spots Artemis 2 moon rocket on the launch pad from space (photo)
description: A NASA astronaut on the ISS captured the Space Launch System rocket for Artemis 2, a mission that aims to bring four astronauts around the moon as soon as Feb. 6.
